 rash, itching, anorexia, nausea, vomiting, fatigue, malaise, right upper quadrant pain, dark urine, pale stools, and jaundice.', 'Synergism', NULL, NULL, 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', 1767317475);
